FindAndReplaceStrings: Strings In Imported Node To Find And Replace
bStripNamespace: Will strip any namespace from the FBX node names
bForceFrontXAxis: Convert the scene from FBX coordinate system to UE coordinate system with front X axis instead of -Y
bConvertSceneUnit: Convert the scene from FBX unit to UE unit(centimeter)
bImportOntoSelectedControls: Whether or not import onto selected controls or all controls
TimeToInsertOrReplaceAnimation: Time that we insert or replace the imported animation
bInsertAnimation: Whether or not we insert or replace, by default we insert
bSpecifyTimeRange: Whether to import over specific Time Range
ControlChannelMappings: Mappings for how Control Rig Control Attributes Map to the incoming Transforms

methods.name: LoadControlMappingsFromPreset
methods.doc: Load the default or metahuman preset into the current mappings
